How to Make a Copy of This Workbook:

- Open the template link
(The sheet will open in “view‑only” mode.)
- In the top‑left corner, click File.
- Select Make a copy.
- Choose a name and a folder in your Google Drive.
- Click Make a copy — your personal version will open automatically.

Then you will have your own fully editable workbook where you can import your transactions, customize categories, and explore the dashboard.
